                        </h5>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapseNine" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="faqNine" data-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            Our platform guarantees your anonymity and prioritizes the safety of students, ensuring your report will be handled with care.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
    
                <!-- FAQ 10 -->
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header" id="faqTen">
                        <h5 class="mb-0">
                            <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseTen" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTen">
                                Can I get support after reporting a bullying incident?
